  "text": "In neuroscience, topographic regularity although does not have a precise definition, it is commonly understood as point-to-point axonal connections among neurons which preserve certain spatial relationships [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . In this section, we translate this definition into a mathematical form and propose a measure to quantify topographic regularity.",
